comment: Whiteside (MIA) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Young (LAL) makes incidental contact with Richardson (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Williams (LAL) makes marginal contact to Richardson (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Russell (LAL) intentionally kicks the ball on the play.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (Miami ball) is confirmed.
Russell (LAL) makes marginal contact with Johnson (MIA) that does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
LATR shows Ingram (LAL) does not make contact with Richardson's (MIA) arm affecting his shot attempt.
Mozgov (LAL) sets the screen on Richardson (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Richardson (MIA) makes contact with the ball before Williams (LAL) retrieves it in the backcourt.
LHH shows Richardson (MIA) makes contact with Williams' (LAL) left arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Whiteside (MIA) sets the screen on Deng (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Winslow (MIA) does not dislodge Robinson (LAL) from his guarding position on the drive to the basket.
Johnson (MIA) makes incidental contact with Robinson (LAL) going for the loose ball.
Young (LAL) commits a take foul on Winslow (MIA).
Deng (LAL) commits a take foul on Dragic (MIA).
